detailedDescription.articleBody: Film, also called movie, motion picture or moving picture, is a visual art-form used to simulate experiences that communicate ideas, stories, perceptions, feelings, beauty, or atmosphere through the use of moving images.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Google Chrome is a cross-platform web browser developed by Google. It was first released in 2008 for Microsoft Windows, and was later ported to Linux, macOS, iOS, and Android where it is the default browser built into the OS.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: Google Chrome Google द्वारा विकसित एक क्रॉस-प्लेटफ़ॉर्म वेब ब्राउज़र है, इसे पहली बार 2008 में माइक्रोसॉफ्ट विंडोज के लिए जारी किया गया था, और बाद में इसे लिनक्स, मैकओएस, आईओएस और एंड्रॉइड में पोर्ट किया गया, जहां यह ओएस में निर्मित डिफ़ॉल्ट ब्राउज़र है।

detailedDescription.articleBody: VK is a Russian online social media and social networking service based in Saint Petersburg. VK is available in multiple languages but it is predominantly used by Russian-speakers.
